PrecisAppointment of NEZHAT KHOSROWSHAHI of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Broadcasting Corporation to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, in the place of Jane Heffelfinger, whose term has expired.
